ideo/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>In Anomaly Collapse, the battlefield is ever-shifting. With abnormal being the new normal, be prepared for bizarre, challenging, and even comical events that will reshape the battlefield's dynamics in a flash. Make flexibility and swift decision-making your most trusted allies!",
